listing.title: Personalized Red Plush Christmas Stocking: Custom Name Decor

Important notice: Orders placed after Dec 9 may not arrive by Christmas due to extended shipping times. Please place your orders early to ensure timely delivery.

Custom name christmas stockings, unforgettable Christmas memories, Everyone can join and enjoy personalized xmas stockings.

Hang it by the fireplace mantel, staircase, or anywhere else that needs a dash of Christmas spirit. This stocking will undoubtedly become a cherished part of your family traditions, year after year.

Spread the magic of Christmas with our Personalized Red Plush Christmas Stocking - a delightful keepsake that captures the essence of the season while celebrating your unique identity.

Each member of the family will love having their very own Red Plush Stocking to hold all of their goodies from Santa.

 Classic Look -- Our red plush stocking with a white cuff is the quintessential Christmas stocking design, a timeless classic
 Great for Any Member of the Family -- When it comes to Christmas stockings, everyone is sure to love this traditional design
 Great Quality -- This stocking is made from a super soft plush material that will be able to hold whatever stocking stuffers you throw in there. The plush will allow the stockings to last for years!

More Details:
Made of plush cotton/polyester fabric with full cuff
